00:16:23.690 --> 00:16:26.030 align:middle line:84%
When it was pointed
out to them, they

00:16:26.030 --> 00:16:28.920 align:middle line:90%
rationalized their decisions.

00:16:28.920 --> 00:16:31.670 align:middle line:84%
They wouldn't
admit that, indeed,

00:16:31.670 --> 00:16:35.530 align:middle line:84%
this woman, just her presence
in front of that automobile,

00:16:35.530 --> 00:16:38.700 align:middle line:90%
predisposed their decision.

00:16:38.700 --> 00:16:40.780 align:middle line:84%
The sophistication
is so good that we

00:16:40.780 --> 00:16:45.850 align:middle line:84%
know if I had a jar of hand
sanitizer on the table,

00:16:45.850 --> 00:16:49.050 align:middle line:84%
and I were to give you
a test, and the test

00:16:49.050 --> 00:16:51.650 align:middle line:84%
was designed to
measure whether you

00:16:51.650 --> 00:16:54.910 align:middle line:84%
were conservative or liberal
in your characteristics,

00:16:54.910 --> 00:16:58.330 align:middle line:84%
your beliefs, that that
jar of hand sanitizer

00:16:58.330 --> 00:17:01.517 align:middle line:84%
would skew you to the
conservative side.

00:17:01.517 --> 00:17:02.600 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Just by using it?

00:17:02.600 --> 00:17:04.380 align:middle line:84%
>>TAYLOR: Just by
having it on the table.

00:17:04.380 --> 00:17:05.380 align:middle line:90%
Now, you think about it.

00:17:05.380 --> 00:17:06.220 align:middle line:90%
Why?

00:17:06.220 --> 00:17:08.819 align:middle line:90%
Well, what is a hand sanitizer?

00:17:08.819 --> 00:17:11.220 align:middle line:90%
It's protection.

00:17:11.220 --> 00:17:12.079 align:middle line:90%
It's conservative.

00:17:12.079 --> 00:17:12.780 align:middle line:90%
It's conscious.

00:17:12.780 --> 00:17:15.619 align:middle line:84%
It's washing your hands and make
sure that there are no germs,

00:17:15.619 --> 00:17:16.490 align:middle line:90%
you see.

00:17:16.490 --> 00:17:21.500 align:middle line:84%
All these little primes
are known so well.

00:17:21.500 --> 00:17:25.010 align:middle line:84%
During Barack Obama's
last campaign,

00:17:25.010 --> 00:17:29.060 align:middle line:84%
