00:32:57.750 --> 00:33:01.260 align:middle line:84%
So you can see that she's about
to put a phallus in her mouth.

00:33:01.260 --> 00:33:05.020 align:middle line:84%
So it becomes very,
very suggestive.

00:33:05.020 --> 00:33:07.590 align:middle line:84%
And when we think
about liquor, we

00:33:07.590 --> 00:33:09.510 align:middle line:84%
typically think
about excitement,

00:33:09.510 --> 00:33:12.920 align:middle line:84%
partying, I'm going to
relax, I'm going to enjoy.

00:33:12.920 --> 00:33:19.470 align:middle line:84%
And so these images in that
context make a big difference.

00:33:19.470 --> 00:33:23.295 align:middle line:84%
Context programming is a huge
part of everything as well.

